@page "/home"

<div class="home-container">
    <h1>Welcome to Our Encryption App</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Secure your files with ease using our powerful encryption tools.</p>

    <div class="services">
        <div class="service-card">
            <h2>Automatic File Encryption</h2>
            <p>
                Our app provides seamless automatic encryption and decryption of your files.
                Simply upload your files, and let our system handle the rest.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
            <h2>Manual File Encryption</h2>
            <p>
                For advanced users, our manual encryption tool allows you to customize
                encryption settings and take full control of the process.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
            <h2>Secure File Exchange</h2>
            <p>
                Send encrypted files to other users securely. They can decrypt the files
                on their end using our app, ensuring end-to-end security.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-company">
        <h2>About Our Company</h2>
        <p>
            At <strong>SecureTech Solutions</strong>, we are dedicated to providing cutting-edge encryption technologies
            to protect your sensitive data. Founded in 2020, our mission is to make encryption accessible and easy to use
            for everyone, from individuals to businesses. With a team of cybersecurity experts, we ensure that our tools
            are not only powerful but also user-friendly.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our app is designed with privacy and security in mind, offering features like automatic and manual encryption,
            as well as secure file sharing. Whether you're a beginner or an advanced user, our tools are tailored to meet
            your needs. Join thousands of satisfied users who trust SecureTech Solutions to keep their data safe.
        </p>
        <div class="company-logo">
            <img src="images/company-logo.png" alt="SecureTech Solutions Logo" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .home-container {
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        background: white; 
        color: #333; 
        min-height: 100vh;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #6e2dc2; 
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        color: #666; 
    }

    .services {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .service-card {
        background: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        width: 300px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); 
        }

        .service-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #6e2dc2; 
        }

        .service-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
        }

    .about-company {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: #f9f9f9; 
        border-radius: 10px;
        text-align: justify; 
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

        .about-company h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #6e2dc2; 
            text-align: center; 
        }

        .about-company p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555; 
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: justify; 
        }

    .company-logo {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        text-align: center; 
    }

        .company-logo img {
            width: 100px; 
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

    /* Responsive */
    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .services {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .service-card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        .about-company {
            padding: 1rem;
        }
    }
</style>

